<h1>Researchers</h1>

<h2>Ray ATARASHI Senior Researcher</h2>

<div class="imageAndText1">
	<p class="imageArea"><a href="index.html"><img src="../image/pic_ray.jpg" alt="Ray ATARASHI Photo" /></a></p>
	<div class="textArea">
		<dl class="researcher">
			<dt>Senior Researcher</dt>
			<dd><span class="name">Ray ATARASHI</span></dd>
		</dl>
		<p>The Internet for your life.</p>
		<p>My research focus is on Advanced network management for new style Internet life.</p>
	</div><!-- /textArea -->
</div><!-- /imageAndText1 -->

